WEBVTT

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:00.000
shaxsan emas, balki YouTubedagi 
holatimni afzal ko'rishdi.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:07.000
(Kulgi)

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:11.000
Bunday kinoyali holatni ortda qoldirgach, 
bu yerda

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:13.000
qandaydir chuqur ma'noli narsa bor edi.

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:15.000
Ularning aytishicha, ular
akasining shaxsan

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:17.000
o'zidan ko'ra, akasining avtomatlashgan

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:19.000
(robotli) turini afzal ko'rishardi.

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:21.000
Avvaliga, bu juda ham his tuyg'usiz

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:24.000
hisoblanadi, lekin ularning nuqtai 
nazaridan o'ylasangiz, juda

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:26.000
ham ma'noli.
Bu holatda ular

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:28.000
mening vaqtimni yo'qotmasdan, akasining

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:31.000
gapini to'xtatib va yana 
takror-takror eshitishi mumkin.